<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome to Beauty Bliss</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

    /* Reset */
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f5f0 0%, #fff 50%, #f8f5f0 100%);
      color: #333;
    }

    a {
      color: #d55fbb;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: #f086d9;
    }

    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      border: 1px solid #e8e2d6;
    }

    .email-header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e1e 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
      padding: 40px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #f086d9;
      position: relative;
    }

    .email-header img {
      width: 160px;
      height: auto;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .email-header h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
      color: #f086d9;
    }

    .email-body {
      padding: 30px 25px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #444;
      background: #fcfaf7;
    }

    .email-body p {
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .email-body a {
      color: #d55fbb;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f086d9 0%, #d55fbb 100%);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 14px 30px;
      border-radius: 50px;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .cta-button:hover {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d55fbb 0%, #f086d9 100%);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(212, 95, 187, 0.3);
    }

    .email-footer {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e1e1e 0%, #2d2d2d 100%);
      padding: 25px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #d55fbb;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .email-footer p {
      margin: 8px 0;
    }

    .email-footer a {
      color: #f086d9;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .email-wrapper {
        margin: 20px;
      }

      .email-header h1 {
        font-size: 22px;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 20px 15px;
      }

      .cta-button {
        padding: 12px 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dkdx7xytz/image/upload/v1723705045/blisslogo1_hefbyn.png" alt="Beauty Bliss Logo">
      <h1>Welcome to Beauty Bliss âœ¨</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
      <p>We are thrilled to welcome you to <strong>Beauty Bliss</strong>, your new go-to destination for all things beauty. We're here to help you discover products that match your style and elevate your beauty routine.</p>
      <p>Stay tuned for exclusive offers, beauty tips, and the latest trends directly in your inbox.</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to <a href="#">contact us</a>.</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining us. Let's make beauty blissful!</p>
      <a href="#" class="cta-button">Explore Our Collection</a>
    </div>

    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>&copy;<%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Beauty Bliss. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="#">Unsubscribe</a> | <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>